examples.en: Claire acknowledged that she was guilty.

He doesn't know Claire's been two-timing him.

examples.en: Claire wished she had primed Sarah beforehand.
examples.ru: Клэр хотелось бы заранее предупредить Сару.

examples.en: Claire made a good match (=married someone suitable).

examples.en: Claire modelled for a few years when she was in her twenties.
examples.ru: Когда Клэр ещё не было тридцати, она несколько лет работала моделью.
